is like, hey, I think that on the fifth book, there's a lot of relationships between Jon

00:14:01.719 --> 00:14:08.159
Snow and also Tyrion and other characters. So check it out. And what she does is she

00:14:08.159 --> 00:14:17.039
shares the dataset using pins by registering a board in the S3 AWS service. And she shares

00:14:17.039 --> 00:14:24.520
this cleanup dataset with Greg and Monica. And what is great is that when Greg hears

00:14:24.520 --> 00:14:30.200
the news, he's like super excited because Greg is not that much interested into doing

00:14:30.200 --> 00:14:34.960
data science, but he's very interested in creating intuitive visualizations that can

