Daenerys Targaryen, like Tyrion Lannister and Cersei. And it's interesting because this

00:15:52.799 --> 00:15:59.820
is just like a different type of skills that is super great looking, intuitive, that anyone

00:15:59.820 --> 00:16:05.280
can understand. Perhaps it's interactive and it really prompts other people to understand

00:16:05.280 --> 00:16:13.119
this data set with the skills from Greg and Darla combined. And sure enough, like Monica

00:16:13.119 --> 00:16:17.760
is also super excited about this. She looks at the data set and is like, wow, I really

00:16:17.760 --> 00:16:23.880
need to get into this. But what goes on her mind is like, I really want to know exactly

