who's the most important character. Is it Jon Snow or is it Daenerys? I want to know

00:16:29.400 --> 00:16:35.799
with a numeric value, which is the most important character. And sure enough, with Pins, she

00:16:35.799 --> 00:16:41.599
can now load the Pins library and retrieve this data set that Darla carefully created

